@@JvXPRenderText
<TITLE JvXPRenderText procedure>
Summary
  Draws text.
Description
  Use JvXPRenderText to either calculate or draw text.
Parameters
  AParent        - The parent of the control to draw.
  ACanvas        - The canvas to draw on.
  ACaption       - The text to draw.
  AFont          - The font to use.
  AEnabled       - Draw text enabled or disabled.
  AShowAccelChar - Draw accelerators or not.
  ARect          - The rect to draw in or adjust according to the parameters.
  AFlags         - Additional flags to use. These are the same flags as used by DrawText.
                  Specifically, if you include DT_CALCRECT in flags, the ARect is adjusted but
                  nothing is drawn.

