@@JvXPFrame3D
<TITLE JvXPFrame3D procedure>
Summary
  Draws a frame on a canvas.
Description
  Use JvXPFrame3D to draw like Frame3D but using an XP style.
Parameters
  ACanvas     - The canvas to draw on.
  Rect        - The rect to draw in. This is adjusted to the dimensions of the rectangle that lies   
              inside the frame.
  TopColor    - The color for the top and left edges.
  BottomColor - The color for the bottom and right edges.
  Swapped     - Set to true if TopColor and BottomColor should swap places.
See Also
  <DELPHILINK Frame3D>

